{"title":"Tax Microdata Benchmarking Review","markdown":{"headingText":"Tax Microdata Benchmarking Review","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n## Overview\n\nThis document tracks development issues and solutions for the tax-microdata-benchmarking project.\n\n## Recent Issues\n\n### SSL Certificate Verification Issue (#354)\n\n**Date:** August 26, 2025  \n**Status:** Fixed via PR\n\n**Problem:**\n- CPS data downloads were failing due to SSL certificate verification errors\n- Error occurred in `tmd/datasets/cps.py` line 176\n- Census Bureau's SSL configuration had compatibility issues with Python/requests/SSL setups\n\n**Solution:**\n- Added `verify=False` to the `requests.get()` call in `tmd/datasets/cps.py`\n- This disables SSL verification for the trusted Census Bureau data source\n- Allows CPS data download process to complete successfully\n\n**Implementation:**\n```python\n# Before\nresponse = requests.get(url, stream=True)\n\n# After  \nresponse = requests.get(url, stream=True, verify=False)\n```\n\n### Tax-Calculator 5.2.0 Compatibility Issue\n\n**Date:** August 26, 2025  \n**Status:** To be addressed in separate issue/PR\n\n**Problem:**\n- Tests fail when using Tax-Calculator version 5.2.0\n- Tests work correctly with Tax-Calculator version 5.1.0\n- Unrelated to the SSL verification fix\n\n**Current Status:**\n- SSL fix PR submitted with Tax-Calculator 5.2.0 as base\n- Tax-Calculator compatibility issue will be addressed separately after SSL fix is merged\n- Allows for independent review and resolution of each issue\n\n## Contributing Guidelines\n\n### Repository Workflow\n\nThis project uses a **trusted contributor model**:\n- Contributors push branches directly to the upstream repository (PSLmodels/tax-microdata-benchmarking)\n- **Do not create forks** - push directly to upstream\n- Create pull requests from branches in the main repository\n\n### Authentication Setup\n\nFor SSH authentication with GitHub:\n\n1. Generate SSH key:\n   ```bash\n   ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C \"your-email@example.com\" -f ~/.ssh/id_ed25519 -N \"\"\n   ```\n\n2. Add public key to GitHub:\n   - Copy contents of `~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub`\n   - Go to GitHub Settings → SSH and GPG keys → New SSH key\n   - Paste key and save\n\n3. Update remote to use SSH:\n   ```bash\n   git remote set-url upstream git@github.com:PSLmodels/tax-microdata-benchmarking.git\n   ```\n\n### Pull Request Process\n\n1. Create feature branch from master\n2. Make changes and commit\n3. Push branch to upstream repository\n4. Create pull request on GitHub\n5. Allow 1-2 days for review\n6. Address any feedback and merge\n\n---\n\n*Last updated: August 26, 2025*","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":"auto","echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":false,"link-external-newwindow":false,"self-contained-math":false,"format-resources":[],"notebook-links":true},"pandoc":{"standalone":true,"wrap":"none","def